    <item>
      <title>印尼因抗议活动放弃修改选举法计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/indonesia-drops-plan-to-revise-election-law-after-protests-m056b0ul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼全国范围内爆发了激烈的抗议活动，并震动了金融市场，此后，印尼议会决定不进行有争议的对地区选举法的修改。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/indonesia-drops-plan-to-revise-election-law-after-protests-m056b0ul</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 11:02:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利威胁将派遣移民前往布鲁塞尔报复欧盟罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/hungary-floats-sending-migrants-to-brussels-to-avenge-eu-fine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利表示，除非能够与欧盟解决其庇护政策处罚方面的争端，否则它可能会开始将出现在其边境的移民直接运送到布鲁塞尔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/hungary-floats-sending-migrants-to-brussels-to-avenge-eu-fine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:24:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
